txt.en: Dulglok is at Shrak Mauruk.\n\nYou should bring the Slug goo to Dulglok.
'I want a tasty meal! Get me some slug goo and maybe I'll share a little with you!\n\n'Just thinking about slugs makes me hungry. Hurry up!'
Bring the Slug goo to Dulglok at Shrak Mauruk
Dulglok commands you to gather some tasty slug goo to feed the war-leaders within Osgiliath.
'Yum! I changed my mind. This goo is just for me and the other war-leaders!'
Slugs can be found in Osgiliath.\n\nYou should collect Slug Goo.
